Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.02,0:22:53.82,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,I keep on trying to find a way out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.82,0:23:00.36,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,But it's ok you don't lock the door anymore
